                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[04.01.2008]</p>
                <p>Animal Welfare: A proposal for a new Norwegian Animal Welfare Act has been released. The consultation paper is available in Norwegian, and a short summary is available in English. The draft Act is available in both languages. The deadline for comments is Monday 18.02.2008.</p>
                
                
